924
00:54:32.686 --> 00:54:34.896
Tu as un peu de sang.

925
00:54:34.980 --> 00:54:36.064
Ouvre les yeux.

926
00:54:41.861 --> 00:54:43.280
Avale.

927
00:54:46.032 --> 00:54:47.701
Oh, la vache.

