00:54:54.040 --> 00:54:55.875
T'es un désastre.

929
00:54:56.793 --> 00:54:58.295
Oh, non !

930
00:54:59.170 --> 00:55:00.046
Arrêtez.

931
00:55:01.548 --> 00:55:04.092
